A vintage-style illustration of an ornate antique magnifying glass hovering over scattered architectural blueprints and technical schematics, rendered in warm sepia tones and aged paper textures. The blueprints show intricate flowcharts and branching tree diagrams with some paths highlighted in faded red ink, suggesting problem areas. Dust motes float in a beam of golden afternoon light streaming through an unseen window. The scene evokes a detective's desk from the 1920s, with brass instruments, an inkwell, and curled paper edges. The magnifying glass creates a subtle distortion effect over the documents beneath it, drawing focus to the complexity of the underlying patterns.
